arts.ttl: Jung the hero as Bremen extinguish Darmstadt's Pokal dreams
arts.sum: DFB-Pokal Round of 16 action continued this evening as Werder Bremen hosted SV Darmstadt at the Weserstadion. The hosts eventually made their dominance count with a 1-0 win at the death.
